			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Default dialogue with the owlbear cub in the player's camp - available after the events of CAMP_OwlbearCub_CFM_Dog. The player can pet the cub, ask some SwA questions and learn what happened during the previous CFM if they opted to quit the dialogue early (what sounded like the owlbear cub attacking the dog was actually the cub having a bad dream and the dog comforting him)." />
